name.jp: ニャングニャングの売り子

description.en: This cute Nyangnyang manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.ar: This cute Nyangnyang manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.br: Esta fofa Nyangnyang gerência uma Loja Pessoal para você! Clique duas vezes para fechar a Loja. Você recebe o item de volta quando a loja é fechada.
description.cns: 可爱彩冠翎猫为您管理个人商店！双击关闭商店。商店关闭后，您可以取回物品。
description.de: Diese niedliche Nyangnyang verwaltet deinen persönlichen Shop für dich. Doppelklicke um deinen Shop zu schließen. Du bekommst deine Gegenstände zurück, wenn du den Shop schließt.

description.fr: Ce mignon Nyangnyang gèrera votre Boutique Personnelle ! Double-cliquez pour fermer la boutique. Vos objets vous seront rendus.
description.id: Nyangnyang yang lucu ini mengelola Personal Shop untuk Anda! Klik dua kali untuk menutup Shop. Anda mendapatkan barang kembali saat Shop tutup.
description.it: This cute Nyangnyang manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.jp: このニャングニャングは、あなたの代わりに個人商店を開いてくれます。使用後はダブルクリックでショップを閉じることができ、アイテムが戻ってきます。
description.kr: 당신을 위해 개인 상점을 관리하는 귀여운 냥냥! 상점을 닫으려면 두 번 클릭하세요. 상점이 닫히면 아이템을 돌려받습니다.

description.sp: ¡Esta linda Nyangnyang administra una Tienda Personal para ti! Haz doble clic para cerrar la Tienda. Recuperarás el objeto cuando se cierre la tienda.

description.th: Nyangnyang น่ารักคนนี้จัดการร้านค้าส่วนตัว ให้คุณ! ดับเบิ้ลคลิกเพื่อปิดร้าน ได้ของคืนเมื่อร้านปิด
description.tw: 可愛的喵娘為你管理個人商店，雙擊可以關閉商店，當商店關閉時物品將會返回
description.vi: Nyangnyang dễ thương này quản lý một Cửa hàng cá nhân cho bạn! Nhấp đúp để đóng Cửa hàng. Bạn nhận lại hàng khi Shop đóng cửa
